<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">« الْبُزَاقُ فِي الْمَسْجِدِ خَطِيئَةٌ وَكَفَّارَتُهَا دَفْنُهَا »</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>